| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1415 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: da5b83c9-bd56-5aa7-b3e0-c4db6b253c1e"
